    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my absolute pride and joy. This car is seriously in incredible shape\u2014it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've taken such good care of it, always garaged and babied. You won't find a single scratch or dent anywhere; it's practically flawless. It drives like a dream and is totally ready for its next adventure. I'm honestly sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it! Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant with individual throttle bodies and a crisp 8,000 RPM redline. This specimen is mechanically superlative: the Vanos system has been overhauled with Beisan components, rod bearings have been replaced, and the rear subframe has been reinforced\u2014addressing all critical platform weak points. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, while the limited-slip M-differential ensures optimal torque distribution. Finished in original paint with zero oxidation, this chassis retains its factory-spec torsional rigidity. A concours-level example for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "2021 Sedan. Mint condition. Single owner. No accidents. Full service history. Garage kept. Smoke-free interior.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
