    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presented in showroom condition, this vehicle is the pinnacle of automotive preservation. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips or swirl marks, further protected by a professionally applied ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of creases, and the original floor mats are pristine. Mechanically, it has been maintained with an open-checkbook policy, documented by a complete binder of service records from day one. Always garage-kept under a breathable cover and never driven in inclement weather, this car drives exactly as it did the day it left the factory floor. Every button, sensor, and feature functions perfectly. This is a rare opportunity for a collector seeking a turn-key, investment-grade example with absolutely no compromises.",
      "price": 48500.0,
